  "keyFeatures": [
    "Cross-platform package manager for Linux, macOS, and Windows",
    "Dynamic package definitions with Lua scripting",
    "Integration with 40+ system and language package managers",
    "Project-specific environments with zoi.yaml",
    "SAT-powered dependency resolution with PubGrub algorithm",
    "Secure package verification with checksums and GPG signatures",
    "Development shells with automatic environment setup",
    "Advanced CLI tools (rollback, pin, exec, doctor, etc.)",
    "Repository-based package distribution system",
    "Library support for embedding in Rust applications"
  ],
